EXTERIOR | Summerhouse 
Lagnö ​Brutalism and natural beauty collide in this striking summer house by Tham & Videgård Arkitekter, located on the Swedish coast. ​
.
​While the striking concrete form is designed to reference traditional boat sheds, paired with extensive glazing the design becomes something much more modern, surprisingly light and airy. ​
.
